properties.jcr:title: Bengawan Solo
properties.shortdescription: Bengawan Solo sells light bites and snacks perfect for tea time. Our local kuehs and confectionery preserve the traditional and homemade quality as we use only the finest ingredients.

properties.shortdescription: Butter Studio, a confectionery shop, was created to honor the spirit of artisan handmade goodness while infusing a uniquely local and playful spin on familiar home-style bakes.

Chewy Junior is a bakery with extraordinary cream puffs. It's crispy on the outside, yet soft & chewy on the inside, making it perfect to munch on! With so many delicious flavours to choose from, you'll be spoilt for choice at Chewy Junior!

Chocolate Origin
properties.shortdescription: Chocolate Origin specialises in chocolate cakes and confectioneries. Using only the best ingredients, we promise you a taste of indulgence with every bite!

properties.shortdescription: Prepared with love, served from our heart.

properties.jcr:title: Eighteen Chefs
properties.shortdescription: Eighteen Chefs is the place to go for affordable Western cuisine with a local twist. As the cherry on top, students, NSFs and senior citizens get to enjoy discounts when dining at this casual Western restaurant!

properties.jcr:title: Four Leaves
properties.shortdescription: Four Leaves is a bakery that provides innovative and quality breads, cake & pastries fresh out of the oven to our customers. Sink your teeth into fluffy buns, delightfully sweet strawberry shortcake & more!

properties.jcr:title: GODIVA Chocolatier
properties.shortdescription: Godiva is easily distinguished by its quality craftsmanship along with superior ingredients like richly flavored Ivory Coast Cocoa Beans, Turkish Filbert Butter & fresh fruit fillings. Each exquisite chocolate creation is beautifully packaged - a feast for your eyes & taste buds.

properties.shortdescription: Hokkaido Baked Cheese Tart

properties.jcr:title: Hong Kong Egglet
properties.shortdescription: Hong Kong Egglet brings to you the iconic Hong Kong street snack but newer, fresher and healthier with our improved recipe.

properties.jcr:title: i Love Taimei
properties.shortdescription: Love all things Taiwanese? The food kiosk I Love Taimei serves up the best of Taiwanese street food culture. Their Signature Crispy Chicken comes in three flavors - Golden Original, Savory BBQ, and Tangy Lemon. Pair it with the Wintermelon Tea TaroQ and you are good to go!

properties.jcr:title: Itacho Sushi
properties.shortdescription: Itacho Sushi restaurant serves an array of authentic Japanese sushi that showcases the freshness and natural sweetness of their premium sashimi. Minimal seasoning is used in the preparation of their sushi so you can taste every note of natural umami.

properties.jcr:title: KFC
properties.shortdescription: Fast food chain KFC's juicy fried chicken keeps fans coming back. The signatures include Original Recipe chicken prepared with Colonel Sander's secret blend of 11 herbs & spices, & the all-time favourite Hot & Crispy chicken.

properties.jcr:title: LeNu Chef Wais Noodle Bar
properties.shortdescription: Welcome to Le Nu Taiwan Beef Noodle Bar. Visit us at Bugis Junction.

properties.jcr:title: Ma Maison
properties.shortdescription: Ma Maison is a Japanese-western fusion restaurant where diners can get together to enjoy original home recipes and warm hospitality. Visit their outlets at Westgate and Junction 8.

properties.jcr:title: McDonald's
properties.shortdescription: When a fast food craving hits, McDonald's is the convenient solution. Try local favourites like McSpicy or McNuggets with the signature Curry Sauce, or all-time favourites like Big Mac & Filet-O-Fish. McCafe also offers a cuppa and dessert.

properties.jcr:title: Miam Miam
properties.shortdescription: Miam Miam dishes up French-Japanese fusion cuisine so you can enjoy the culinary creations from the East & West. Indulge in the decadent lobster bisque spaghetti or the famous fluffy & sweet souffle pancakes!

Mincheng Bibimbap   is a renowned establishment specializing in Chinese Korean ethnic cuisine, offering a unique blend of flavors that reflect the rich culinary heritage of the Yanbian Korean Autonomous Prefecture in China. Since its inception in 2008, Mincheng has expanded globally with over 400 outlets worldwide.   Our menu boasts a diverse range of dishes, with the iconic Mincheng Bibimbap taking center stage. In addition to this signature dish, we offer Stone Plate series and a selection of savory soups inspired by Chinese Korean traditions. Complementing these are complimentary offerings like Rice Kimchi and seaweed soup, ensuring a complete and satisfying dining experience. Explore the flavours of Chinese Korean cuisine today.
properties.jcr:title: Mincheng Bibimbap
Monster Curry
properties.shortdescription: Monster Curry is a Japanese restaurant chain in Singapore that specialises in Japanese curry served with a demi-glace curry sauce. Visit its outlet at Bugis Junction today.

properties.jcr:title: Mr Bean
properties.shortdescription: Mr Bean is a food kiosk that offers a variety of soya bean drinks and snacks. Young and old can enjoy refreshing ice blended flavoured soya drinks, ice cream, pastry & more.
MRS BANANA
properties.jcr:title: MRS BANANA
Nam Kee JB Handmade Pau
properties.shortdescription: At Nam Kee Pau, a food kiosk, all pau items are handmade in house. Sink your teeth into soft steamy buns bursting with sweet velvety lotus paste and other delicious fillings. If you are craving for something more filling, indulge in a hearty serving of Mee Hoon Kuay.

properties.jcr:title: Nando's
properties.shortdescription: Fire up your taste buds with some PERi delicious goodness! Hailing from South Africa, Nandos is an award-winning chain blazing across the world with its Afro-Portuguese flame-grilled PERi-PERi Chicken.

properties.jcr:title: Nunsaram Korean Dessert Cafe
properties.shortdescription: One of the pioneers of Korean Bingsoo in Singapore, Nunsaram is a dessert bar that offers 15 icy creations with flavors authentic to this wildly popular Korean dessert. With classics like Injeolmi & locally adapted flavors like Milo, beat the heat with their refreshing sweet treats.

properties.jcr:title: Old Chang Kee
properties.shortdescription: Famous for its curry puffs that are filled with perfectly spiced curry potatoes, chicken and egg, Old Chang Kee has expanded its menu to include a variety of finger foods & light bites that can curb those hunger pangs on the go!

PARIS BAGUETTE Cafe
properties.shortdescription: Paris Baguette is one of South Korea's most famous bakeries, known for its high quality baked goods and dedicated customer service.

properties.shortdescription: Seoul Garden is a Korean Barbecue restaurant with buffet-styled grill and steamboat-dining. Outlets are found in CapitaLand mall like Tampines mall & Bugis Junction.

properties.shortdescription: No more travelling to Taiwan just for their Giant Fried Chicken or Oyster Mee Sua because Snackz It is bringing it right to Singapore for you. Serving your favorite Taiwanese night market signatures and other snacks like Tempura and Sweet Potato Fritters, Snackz It takes fried food to the next level.
properties.jcr:title: Snackz It!
Starbucks
properties.shortdescription: Starbucks Coffee is the premier roaster & retailer of the highest quality arabica coffee in the world. Through our unwavering commitment to excellence & our guiding principles, we bring the unique Starbucks Experience to life for every customer through every cup.

properties.jcr:title: stuff'd
properties.shortdescription: Stuff'd is a food kiosk that prepares deliciously grilled, naturally marinated chicken hand-rolled into an exploding wrap bursting with healthy greens and flavor. Get stuffed with this delicious mix of nutritional natural goodness.

properties.jcr:title: Subway
properties.shortdescription: Subway is a fast food restaurant serving sandwiches, wraps and salads. Enjoy gourmet cold cut deli on herbs-infused bread with a generous serving of nutritious greens drizzled with decadent low fat dressings.

properties.jcr:title: Sushi Plus
properties.shortdescription: A word play of  , Sushi Plus is a new contemporary sushi dining concept from Sushi Express that redefines the conventional conveyor belt sushi with state-of-art technology integration. By delicately balancing quality with affordability, Sushi Plus aims to be the pinnacle of casual dining for Japanese cuisine.

properties.jcr:title: Swensen's
properties.shortdescription: Satisfy your cravings at Swensen's, the Western restaurant with a wide selection of hearty food, sundaes & ice cream cakes! Try signatures like Fish & Chips, Mac 'N' Cheese & locally-inspired Crab Meat Fried Rice! End your meal on a sweet note with Swensen's favorite sundaes like Sticky Chewy Chocolate or Banana Split!
Fresh pasta to go.
properties.jcr:title: Tangled Fresh Pasta To Go
TANYU
properties.shortdescription: TANYU specialises in grilled fish in over 70 major cities in China with more than 240 outlets. TANYU opened its first overseas flagship store in Singapore on 8 Dec 2017. In order to cater to the diverse tastes of local Singaporeans, TANYU makes use of a variety of cooking methods and offers 12 kinds of flavors for it grilled fish, such as sweet and savory spicy, salted, roasted, etc

properties.jcr:title: The Coffee Bean & Tea Leaf
properties.shortdescription: The Coffee Bean & Tea Leaf is the oldest and largest specialty coffee and tea retailer in the United States, known for sourcing and providing the finest ingredients and flavors from around the world. The Coffee Bean & Tea Leaf is also Halal-Certified.

properties.jcr:title: Tip Top
properties.shortdescription: Tip Top Curry Puffs are made with 18 specially handpicked blends of spices, premium potatoes and ingredients. Together with their signature pastry skin, you will be assured of a rich and flavorful experience in every bite.

properties.jcr:title: TOAST BOX
properties.shortdescription: Toast Box is a coffeeshop favoured by locals. Come in and sit down for a fragrant cup of Nanyang coffee and toast, along with other local Singpaore delights.

Hailing from Nagoya, TORI SANWA is known for their delicious chicken dishes. Be sure to try their top dishes: Aburi Oyako Don, Oyako Don, Negi Shio Tori Soba, Chicken Teriyaki Hitsumabushi, Chicken Karaage Rice Set
properties.jcr:title: TORI SANWA
Tori-Q
properties.shortdescription: Tori Q transforms simple chicken chunks on sticks into chargrilled goodness on a stick with their Yakitori selection. Generously coated with their special Tare sauce to give that savory sweet caramelization, Tori Q is a BBQ upgrade.

properties.jcr:title: WOK HEY
properties.shortdescription: If you like a good dish that brings out the heat and aroma of the wok, head down to the food kiosk Wok Hey, and experience the true stir fry with our signature Fried Rice, Ramen & Udon with your selection of toppings like Tobiko and Sous Vide Egg.

properties.jcr:title: XiaoLongKan Hotpot
properties.shortdescription: Famous traditional Chinese XiaoLongKan Hotpot Restaurant has arrived in Singapore, bringing to you the best authentic Sichuan-style spicy hotpot!

properties.jcr:title: Ya Kun Kaya Toast
properties.shortdescription: Serving humble fare of coffee, tea, egg & toast, Ya Kun Kaya Toast is a cafe that exemplifies how less is more. The bread is generously slathered with our special kaya recipe that's stood the test of time. Get your breakfast fix.

properties.jcr:title: YOSHINOYA
properties.shortdescription: Enjoy a quick & balanced meal of protein and greens at Yoshinoya. With a wide selection of rice bowls that come wth a generous serving of vegetables, choose from all-time favorites such as the Teriyaki Chicken Don & Beef Don.
